Class RightScalarMultiplicationNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • fi.arithmeticvisualizer.logic.nodes.Node
      • fi.arithmeticvisualizer.logic.nodes.BinaryNode
        • fi.arithmeticvisualizer.logic.nodes.RightScalarMultiplicationNode

  • public class RightScalarMultiplicationNode
extends BinaryNode
    A RightScalarMultiplicationNode is a BinaryNode that performs scalar multiplication from the right.
